title: Travis Barker Gushes About New Girlfriend Ora: 'She's Stunning'
text: Brand new couple Rita Ora and Travis Barker posed together while attending Halloween Horror Nights at Universal Studios Hollywood on Sunday (October 4). The 39-year-old Blink 182 drummer opened up about his relationship with the 24-year-old entertainer, who he met at the Power 106 All-Star Game in L.A. on September 20. “I performed there with [...] »
